Dr. Chemical's Lab
==================

Entry in PyWeek #14  <http://www.pyweek.org/14/>
URL: http://pyweek.org/e/tboxthonton
Team: T Box Thon Ton
Members: superjoe, Squish
License: see LICENSE



"In Dr. Chem's Lab... physics struggles with YOU"


Running the Game
----------------

    Install Dependencies on Linux:

        sudo pip install pymunk pyglet

    Install Dependencies on OSX:

      Install pymunk, avbin, and pyglet from source:

        svn checkout http://pymunk.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ pymunk-read-only
        cd pymunk-read-only
        python setup.py build_chipmunk
        sudo python setup.py install

        Untested:
            wget https://github.com/downloads/AVbin/AVbin/avbin-src-7.tar.gz
            tar xzvf avbin-src-7.tar.gz
            cd avbin-src-7
            ./configure
            make
            sudo make install

        hg clone https://pyglet.googlecode.com/hg/ pyglet
        cd pyglet
        sudo python setup.py install

    Install Dependencies on Windows:

        Untested:

            Install http://pyglet.googlecode.com/files/pyglet-1.1.4.msi
            Install http://code.google.com/p/pymunk/downloads/list


    Run:

        python run_game.py

    Alternate keyboard layouts:

        python run_game.py --dvorak
        python run_game.py --colemak

    Disable networking (prevents crashes in 1player mode):

        python run_game.py --survival

    Disable sound efects (removes dependecy on AVBin):

        python run_game.py --nofx


How to Play the Game
--------------------

    Start the game and click Controls. It will tell you how to play.
